  <div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><b>Benzodiazepine Dosage Converter</b></h2>
      <br>
      <h4>This is a simple tool made to help you figure out how much of a given benzodiazepine dose converts into another benzodiazepine dose. Please make sure to research the substances thoroughly before using them. </h4>
      <h4>A good idea is to compare the effects of the two different benzodiazepines, as even though the dose is 'similiar' you might not get the effects you're used to.</h4>
      <br>
      <div class="bs-callout bs-callout-danger">
        <h4><b>Important</b>: Equivalent doses may be inaccurate for larger quantities of benzos with different effect profiles. Please compare the dosages below to see weighted dosage ranges.</h4></div>
      <form action="" method="POST" name="calcform" type="post" class="">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="form-inline">
            <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-md-6">
              <h3 class="center">
                I have  <input type="text" name="dose" value="0" size="8" oninput="calculate()" class="form-control">  mg of 
               <select name="inputSubstance" class="form-control" id="inputSubstance"  onchange="newInput();"> </select>
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-xs-12 col-md-6">
              <h3 class="center">
              I want to know the dose for 
              <select name="outputSubstance" class="form-control"  id="outputSubstance" onchange="newOutput();"> </select>
             </h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6" id="inputInfo">
            <ul class="list-group">
              <li class="list-group-item active ">
                <h3>Start dose:  <span id="inputDoseResult">0</span> mg of <a href="http://drugs.tripsit.me/alprazolam"  id="inputName">Alprazolam</a></h3></li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <h4>Summary:</h4> </li>
              <li class="list-group-item" id="inputSummary"></li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
